474
00:46:25,600 --> 00:46:29,200
Is that a business model [inaudible]?
We should do as much as needed,  

475
00:46:29,200 --> 00:46:34,160
as little as possible.
So we invest in our ecosystem  

476
00:46:34,160 --> 00:46:41,760
